title: World of Warcraft / english / 1-10
description:
on English

World of Warcraft: Volume 1 and Volume 2, is the first story arc in a series of comics about the mysterious gladiator Lo'Gosh, trying to survive gladiatorial battles and to discover his forgotten past, among the fantastic background of the popular series and MMO, World of Warcraft.

Volume 1:
Issue 0 - Prologue
Issue 1 - Stranger in a Strange Land
Issue 2 - Killing Ground
Issue 3 - Destiny Awaits!
Issue 4 - Balancing the Scales
Issue 5 - The Beast Within!
Issue 6 - Blood
Issue 7 - Revelations

Written by Walter Simonson, Art by Ludo Lullabi and Sandra Hope, Covers by Jim Lee, Samwise Didier.
Contains Issues #0-7 plus an Exclusive Preview.

World of Warcraft: Volume 2, is the second story arc in a series of comics about the mysterious gladiator Lo'Gosh, trying to survive gladiatorial battles and to discover his forgotten past, among the fantastic background of the popular series and MMO, World of Warcraft.

Written by Walter Simonson, Art by Ludo Lullabi and Sandra Hope, Covers by Jim Lee, Samwise Didier.


on Russian

Mir Warcraft, komiks jepopeja o pohozhdenijah tainstvennogo gladiatora po imeni Lo'Gosh, kotoryj pytaetsja vspomnit' svojo proshloe do gladiatorskih bojov, i vsjo jeto razvivaetsja v fantasticheskih realjah mira Warcraft.
Podrobnee mozhno oznakomitsja na portale Rucomics.info
